Package: linux-battery-tray
Version: 1.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, upower, libnotify-bin, power-profiles-daemon, brightnessctl
Maintainer: tyy130 <tyy130@example.com>
Description: Lightweight system tray battery indicator
 A lightweight, reliable system tray battery indicator for Linux using Python and GTK3.
 Provides real-time battery status, notifications, and detailed information via a dropdown menu.
 Features brightness control, power profiles, and battery health monitoring.
